tik im Mittelpunkt der Überlegungen stehen. Norman Braun ist Professor für Soziologie an der Universität München.  aIssued also in print.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn German.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 01. Dez 2022) 0aSocial SciencesxPolitical SciencexPolitical Science, other. 0aSocial SciencesxSociologyxSociology, other. 4aDrogenpolitik. 4aRational Choice. 7aSOCIAL SCIENCE / Sociology / General.2bisacsh08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertDGBA Social Sciences 2000 - 2014z9783110638080oZDB-23-GSS0 cprintz978348656645140uhttps://doi.org/10.1515/978348683324940uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9783486833249423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/document/cover/isbn/9783486833249/original  aEBA_BACKALL  aEBA_CL_SN  aEBA_DGALL  aEBA_EBKALL  aEBA_SSHALL  aEBA_STMALL  aGBV-deGruyter-alles  aPDA11SSHE  aPDA12STME  aPDA5EBK  aZDB-23-GSSc2000d2014